24namespace webrtc {
25
26std::vector<SdpVideoFormat> InternalDecoderFactory::GetSupportedFormats()
27 const {
28 std::vector<SdpVideoFormat> formats;
29 formats.push_back(SdpVideoFormat(cricket::kVp8CodecName));
30 for (const SdpVideoFormat& format : SupportedVP9DecoderCodecs())
31 formats.push_back(format);
32 for (const SdpVideoFormat& h264_format : SupportedH264Codecs())
33 formats.push_back(h264_format);
34 if (kIsLibaomAv1DecoderSupported)
35 formats.push_back(SdpVideoFormat(cricket::kAv1CodecName));
36 return formats;
37}
38
39std::unique_ptr<VideoDecoder> InternalDecoderFactory::CreateVideoDecoder(
40 const SdpVideoFormat& format) {
41 if (!format.IsCodecInList(GetSupportedFormats())) {
42 RTC_LOG(LS_WARNING) << "Trying to create decoder for unsupported format. "
43 << format.ToString();
44 return nullptr;
45 }
46
47 if (absl::EqualsIgnoreCase(format.name, cricket::kVp8CodecName))
48 return VP8Decoder::Create();
49 if (absl::EqualsIgnoreCase(format.name, cricket::kVp9CodecName))
50 return VP9Decoder::Create();
51 if (absl::EqualsIgnoreCase(format.name, cricket::kH264CodecName))
52 return H264Decoder::Create();
53 if (kIsLibaomAv1DecoderSupported &&
54 absl::EqualsIgnoreCase(format.name, cricket::kAv1CodecName))
55 return CreateLibaomAv1Decoder();
56
57 RTC_NOTREACHED();
58 return nullptr;
59}
